SUMMARY:LAW OF ATTRACTION: Live the Life You Truly Wish To Live! (Sunday M
 arch 29th) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 Please join us for an inspiring\, interactive and insightful afternoon as 
 we continue to move closer to living the life we wish to live using the am
 azing and miraculous Law of Attraction.\n\nWe're going to have a lot of fu
 n too!\n\n\\*Joined by my other personal growth and social groups too\; so
  we can anticipate a terrific turn out\, with wonderful like minded people
 \n\n**Date:**\nSunday\, March 29th 2026\n**Arrival Time:**\nArrive between
  4:00 pm and 4:30 pm\n**Where to Meet us?**\n**Location: La Carnita - Good
  Fortune Bar (Main Floor)**\n**Address:** 130 Eglinton Ave. Toronto\, ON M
 4P 2X9\n**Free Parking:** on Eglinton and Residential area\n**Yonge and Eg
 linton Subway:** (Very close\, 3 minute walking distance)\n\nEvent Details
  below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\nE
 vent Details:\n**LAW OF ATTRACTION: Live the Life You Truly Wish To Live!*
 *\n**(Sunday\, March 29th)**\n\n-Take your life to the next level with inc
 reased clarity\, joy\, fulfillment\, abundance and peace\n-Deepen your und
 erstanding on how to apply the **Law of Attraction** so it works in all ar
 eas of your life (Personal\, Professional\, Social & Romantic)\n-Develop y
 our confidence and sense of self so you are more open to receive what the 
 universe wants to give you\n-Tap into your inner source of passions\, tale
 nts and creativity that will guide you to a life beyond your wildest imagi
 nation *(And then ask the Universe for even more!)*\n\n\\*Interactive\, in
 spiring and insightful afternoon designed to help you live the life you tr
 uly desire and truly deserve to live (with greater flow\, energy\, ease an
 d purpose)\n\n\\*This event will be effectively facilitated with powerful 
 insights\, useful tools\, practical exercises and group participation\n\n\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n***Our Ins
 tructor/Facilitator:***\n**Steve Flemming** is the founder of **Soul City 
 Social Club since 2006.** He produces monthly events on subjects involving
  personal/spiritual growth\, modern dating and healthy relationships while
  incorporating the **Law of Attraction and other useful tools.** Each even
 t is designed to help you experience greater joy\, inner peace\, confidenc
 e\, fulfillment\, love\, meaning and aliveness in our lives. Steve is a pr
 ofessional group Facilitator and Inspirational Speaker. Steve has an ongoi
 ng passion to help shift people's lives and consciousness for the better i
 n areas that matter most to you.\nhttps://www.meetup.com/SoulCity/\n\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\n**When to arrive: (Ask for Steve when you arrive-or head to b
 ack area)**\n-Please arrive between 4:00 pm and 4:30 pm (to get registered
  and settled in)\n-The formal part of the afternoon will start shortly aft
 er 4:30 p.m. and go until roughly 6:30 p.m.\n-Stick around after for more 
 mingling and our dinner party (optional)\n\\*no extra charge for attending
  the dinner party event\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Event Fee:** 10 dollars upon arriva
 l (HST included)\n(Cash only when you arrive or in advance by e transfer t
 o- steveflemming11@gmail.com\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\\*Lunch/Dinner & Beverage M
 enu available too\n\\*Includes reserved seating for the group\n\\*At least
  one Beverage and/or appetizer minimum to support the staff and venue\n\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Park
 ing Available:**\n\\*Plenty of free street parking on Eglinton and (Reside
 ntial area south/east of venue for free)\n**Close to Subway Station:**\n\\
 *Also very close to the the Yonge/Eglinton subway station\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
